     font-size:0.95em;
     line-height:1.4;">
  <strong>🩵 Supportive‑Conversation Trainer’s Reference Sheet</strong><br>
  Version 1.0  |  Last Updated:  <span id="update-date"></span>  |  License:  Creative Commons BY‑NC 4.0<br>
  <em>Purpose: models supportive, non‑clinical communication practices for helper training.</em>
</div>

<script>
  // Fill the date field automatically (ISO style)
  const d = new Date();
  document.getElementById("update-date").textContent =
      d.getFullYear() + "-" + String(d.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,"0") + "-" + String(d.getDate()).padStart(2,"0");
</script>
```

