- Works in standard browsers and LMS webviews without external libraries.  
- If you prefer a literal static date (for version control), just replace the JavaScript lines with the hard‑coded date.  
- The inline style ensures it displays legibly even if external CSS fails to load; you can later move the rules to your stylesheet under `#module-banner { … }`.

